OL,3,CPraise and criticism for Drakeford in
OL,4,CCovid inquiry report
OL,6,FThe UK Covid-19 inquiry praised the
OL,7,F"careful and considerate" approach of
OL,8,FMark Drakeford during the pandemic but
OL,9,Fhighlighted a series of errors made by
OL,10,Fthe Welsh Government.
OL,12,FThe then-First Minister choosing a St
OL,13,FDavid's Day event over attending a
OL,14,FCabinet meeting, allowing two
OL,15,FStereophonics gigs to continue, and "a
OL,16,Flack of trust" between the then-Prime
OL,17,FMinister Boris Johnson and the First
OL,18,FMinisters of the devolved nations were
OL,19,Fall criticised in the report.
