OL,3,CPraise and criticism for Drakeford in
OL,4,CCovid inquiry report
OL,6,FThe inquiry found response to the
OL,7,FCovid pandemic was "a repeated case of
OL,8,Ftoo little, too late" by all four UK
OL,9,Fgovernments.
OL,11,FIn its second of 10 reports, the
OL,12,Finquiry accused the Welsh Government,
OL,13,Falong with the other devolved nations,
OL,14,Fof failing to take timely and
OL,15,Feffective action and being too reliant
OL,16,Fon the UK Government to lead the
OL,17,Fresponse.
