OL,3,CPraise and criticism for Drakeford in
OL,4,CCovid inquiry report
OL,6,FHowever, it praised the "careful,
OL,7,Fconsidered and compassionate" approach
OL,8,Fof then-First Minister Mark Drakeford,
OL,9,Fcompared to what it described as a
OL,10,F"toxic and chaotic culture" at the
OL,11,Fcentre of the UK Government.
OL,13,FThe report, published on Thursday, 20
OL,14,FNovember, investigated political
OL,15,Fdecision-making during the pandemic
OL,16,Fand included evidence from Welsh
OL,17,Fministers, experts and people affected.
