OL,3,CPraise and criticism for Drakeford in
OL,4,CCovid inquiry report
OL,6,FChair Baroness Hallett made 19
OL,7,Frecommendations to better protect the
OL,8,FUK from future pandemics and improve
OL,9,Fdecision-making in a crisis.
OL,11,F"All four governments failed to
OL,12,Fappreciate the scale of the threat or
OL,13,Fthe urgency of response it demanded,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
OL,16,F"When they did realise the scale of
OL,17,Fthe threat, politicians and
OL,18,Fadministrators in the UK government
OL,19,Fand the devolved administrations were
OL,20,Fpresented with unenviable choices as
OL,21,Fto how to respond.
