OL,3,CPraise and criticism for Drakeford in
OL,4,CCovid inquiry report
OL,6,F"Whatever decision they took there was
OL,7,Foften no right answer or good outcome.
OL,8,FThey also had to make decisions in
OL,9,Fconditions of extreme pressure.
OL,10,FNonetheless, I can summarise my
OL,11,Ffindings of the response as 'too
OL,12,Flittle, too late'."
OL,14,FThe emerging threat
OL,16,FThe report criticised all four UK
OL,17,Fgovernments for failing to recognise
OL,18,Fthe emerging threat of Covid.
