OL,3,CPraise and criticism for Drakeford in
OL,4,CCovid inquiry report
OL,6,FIn January 2020, when there were
OL,7,F"clear signs of the virus's growing
OL,8,Fthreat" around the world, Welsh
OL,9,Fministers were instead focusing on
OL,10,FBrexit, budget concerns and adverse
OL,11,Fweather.
OL,13,FDays after the first case was
OL,14,Fidentified in Wales in late February
OL,15,F2020, the First Minister chose to
OL,16,Fattend a St David's Day event in
OL,17,FBrussels rather than a Welsh Cabinet
OL,18,Fmeeting.
