OL,3,CPraise and criticism for Drakeford in
OL,4,CCovid inquiry report
OL,6,FThis was despite Mr Drakeford claiming
OL,7,FCovid was the Welsh Government's
OL,8,Fpriority at the time.
OL,10,FThe report said by this point it
OL,11,Fshould have been apparent to all First
OL,12,FMinisters that Covid-19 was the most
OL,13,Fpressing issue facing their
OL,14,Fgovernments.
OL,16,FWhile being advised to find
OL,17,F"nightingale type wards" for isolating
OL,18,FCovid patients, mass gatherings
OL,19,Fcontinued in Wales, including two
OL,20,FStereophonics gigs in Cardiff.
