OL,6,FA Six Nations match between Wales and
OL,7,FScotland at the Principality Stadium
OL,8,Fwas cancelled just one day in advance
OL,9,Fby the Welsh Rugby Union.
OL,11,FBut this was based on advice from
OL,12,FPublic Health Wales and not the Welsh
OL,13,FGovernment, which did not intervene -
OL,14,Fa decision then-Health Minister
OL,15,FVaughan Gething told the inquiry now
OL,16,F"jars".
