OL,3,CPraise and criticism for Drakeford in
OL,4,CCovid inquiry report
OL,6,FBaroness Hallett said the decision to
OL,7,Fimpose a lockdown was "as difficult a
OL,8,Fdecision as any UK government or
OL,9,Fdevolved administration has ever had
OL,10,Fto make".
OL,12,FGovernments had to weigh up public
OL,13,Fhealth benefits against the social,
OL,14,Feconomic and educational harm. But she
OL,15,Fsaid "inadequate planning, data and
OL,16,Fstrategy" made that "a great deal
OL,17,Fharder".
