OL,3,CPraise and criticism for Drakeford in
OL,4,CCovid inquiry report
OL,6,FThe report added that it would not
OL,7,Fhave been practical for the devolved
OL,8,Fadministrations to announce a
OL,9,Fmandatory lockdown before the UK
OL,10,FGovernment did so.
OL,12,FThe inquiry found the Welsh
OL,13,FGovernment's decision to ease lockdown
OL,14,Frestrictions more gradually than in
OL,15,FEngland in the summer of 2020 reduced
OL,16,Fthe potential need for more lockdowns.
