OL,3,CPraise and criticism for Drakeford in
OL,4,CCovid inquiry report
OL,6,FDespite being advised that further
OL,7,Frestrictions were needed in October,
OL,8,Fthe Welsh Government was criticised
OL,9,Ffor delaying the implementation of a
OL,10,Ftwo-week 'firebreak'.
OL,12,FBetween August to December 2020, Wales
OL,13,Fhad the highest age-standardised
OL,14,Fmortality rate of the four nations.
OL,15,FThe report said it is likely that this
OL,16,Fwas the result of a combination of
OL,17,Ffailed local restrictions, imposing
OL,18,Fthe firebreak too late and the
OL,19,Fdecision to relax measures more
OL,20,Fquickly than scientists advised.
