OL,3,CPraise and criticism for Drakeford in
OL,4,CCovid inquiry report
OL,6,FScientific advice
OL,8,FDuring the pandemic governments were
OL,9,Fadvised by expert groups made up of
OL,10,Fscientists, doctors and other
OL,11,Fspecialists.
OL,13,FThe report raised concerns about a
OL,14,Flack of diversity within Wales'
OL,15,Fadvisory group, which sometimes led to
OL,16,Finsufficient challenge in discussions.
OL,18,FIt also found many members were
OL,19,Fvolunteering their time and not paid
OL,20,Ffor their work.
