OL,4,CCovid inquiry report
OL,6,FRelationship between the Welsh and UK
OL,7,FGovernment
OL,9,FThe Welsh Government was praised for
OL,10,Fhaving a "fully engaged, effective and
OL,11,Finclusive" Cabinet during the pandemic.
OL,13,FThe report said the use of the Cabinet
OL,14,Ffor making decisions enabled the Welsh
OL,15,FGovernment to make "transparent and
OL,16,Fcollective decisions".
