OL,6,FIt was agreed that the relatively
OL,7,Flimited number of attendees of Welsh
OL,8,FCabinet meetings enabled the Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment to work in a highly
OL,10,Fintegrated way and make decisions at
OL,11,Fpace.
OL,13,FHowever, the report highlighted a
OL,14,Fnumber of issues with the way the
OL,15,FWelsh Government and other devolved
OL,16,Fadministrations worked with the UK
OL,17,FGovernment.
