OL,3,CPraise and criticism for Drakeford in
OL,4,CCovid inquiry report
OL,6,F"A lack of trust" between the then-
OL,7,FPrime Minister Boris Johnson and the
OL,8,FFirst Ministers and Deputy Ministers
OL,9,Fof the devolved nations "coloured the
OL,10,Fapproach to involving them in UK
OL,11,Fgovernment decision-making".
OL,13,FBaroness Hallett said "it is incumbent
OL,14,Fon politicians to work collectively"
OL,15,Fin future and recommended "urgent
OL,16,Freform" to structures for decision-
OL,17,Fmaking.
