OL,3,CPraise and criticism for Drakeford in
OL,4,CCovid inquiry report
OL,6,FThe report highlighted inconsistencies
OL,7,Fin the way those caught breaking Covid
OL,8,Frules and laws were punished across
OL,9,Fthe UK.
OL,11,FIn Wales and England, some individuals
OL,12,Ffaced #10,000 fines, while in
OL,13,FScotland, most fines were just #60.
OL,15,FIt also found enforcement
OL,16,Fdisproportionately affected younger
OL,17,Fmen and ethnic minority groups in
OL,18,FWales.
