OL,3,CPraise and criticism for Drakeford in
OL,4,CCovid inquiry report
OL,6,FOn a number of occasions during the
OL,7,Fpandemic, the report said decision-
OL,8,Fmakers and their advisers across the
OL,9,FUK appeared to have broken rules.
OL,11,FUnlike in England, Scotland and
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland there was just one
OL,13,Fallegation in Wales - when Vaughan
OL,14,FGething was pictured with his child
OL,15,Feating chips on a park bench.
OL,17,FBaroness Hallett said it is not for
OL,18,Fthe inquiry to investigate such
OL,19,Fallegations, but said rule-breaking
OL,20,Fundermined public confidence in
OL,21,Fdecision-making.
