OL,3,CPraise and criticism for Drakeford in
OL,4,CCovid inquiry report
OL,6,FPublic messaging
OL,8,FThe Welsh Government held ore than 230
OL,9,Fpress conferences during the pandemic,
OL,10,Foften using these to announce
OL,11,Fsignificant developments.
OL,13,FThese were commended for their
OL,14,Faccessibility, with a BSL interpreter
OL,15,Fattending every one. Later steps to
OL,16,Fensure key messages were available in
OL,17,Fdifferent languages were also
OL,18,Frecognised.
