OL,3,CPraise and criticism for Drakeford in
OL,4,CCovid inquiry report
OL,6,FHowever, the report said public
OL,7,Fmessaging across the four nations was
OL,8,Foften confusing and inconsistent.
OL,10,FDifferences in face mask rules caused
OL,11,Fparticular confusion, with one
OL,12,Finstance where passengers on trains
OL,13,Ffrom London to Cardiff were required
OL,14,Fto wear a face mask until reaching
OL,15,FNewport, after which they could remove
OL,16,Fit.
