OL,3,CPraise and criticism for Drakeford in
OL,4,CCovid inquiry report
OL,6,FThe UK Government's decision to run
OL,7,Fits 'Stay Alert' campaign across all
OL,8,Ffour nations "risked undermining the
OL,9,Fcontinued advise to stay at home in
OL,10,FWales, Scotland and Northern Ireland".
OL,12,FWales was praised for its 'Keep Wales
OL,13,FSafe' slogan which was described as
OL,14,F"effective".
OL,16,FThe report also commended the Welsh
OL,17,FGovernment's "more cautious" approach
OL,18,Fto public-facing communications, such
OL,19,Fas Mark Drakeford's continued warning
